comment: Jefferson (BKN) loses his balance and there is incidental contact with Tucker (PHO) that causes both players to fall to the ground.
Young (BKN) makes contact to the body that affects Knight's (PHO) play to the basket.
Morris (PHO) grabs Lopez (BKN) as he tries to roll to the basket after setting the screen and the contact affects his FOM.
Morris (PHO) is outside the Restricted Area and establishes himself in a legal guarding position before Williams (BKN) begins his upward shooting motion.
Morris (PHO) dislodges Williams (BKN) to establish better position to receive the entry pass.
Young (BKN) sets the screen on Knight (PHO) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Lopez (BKN) gives Morris (PHO) room to land and the contact after the jump shot is incidental.
Johnson (BKN) pushes off Tucker (PHO) to create space on the jump shot.
Jack (BKN) makes contact with Bledsoe's (PHO) arm and the contact affects his play to the basket.
Morris (PHO) contests the shot attempt by Johnson (BKN) and there is incidental contact after the shot is released.
Morris (PHO) does not establish himself in a legal guarding position when Jack (BKN) starts his upward shooting motion.
Jack (BKN) makes contact with Knight's (PHO) arm after the shot is released and it has no affect on his follow-through.
Bogdanovic (BKN) does not inbound the ball within the allotted 5-second time limit.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court was overturned and possession was awarded to PHX.
Williams (BKN) commits a take foul on Bledsoe (PHO).
Williams (BKN) commits a take foul on Bledsoe (PHO).
Jack (BKN) commits a take foul on Wright (PHO).
